246
00:12:25,770 --> 00:12:27,950
[Memorial from Marquis Zhongyi, Gu Yunnian]

247
00:12:45,780 --> 00:12:47,630
It's a five-colored glazed jar.

248
00:12:48,270 --> 00:12:49,270
His Highness and I

249
00:12:49,270 --> 00:12:51,150
