250
00:12:52,150 --> 00:12:53,030
Anyhow,

251
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:54,990
just the grand occasion today

252
00:12:55,270 --> 00:12:55,780
feels like

253
00:12:55,780 --> 00:12:57,630
