254
00:12:58,630 --> 00:13:00,270
Official Ren, you're a wise woman.

255
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:00,990
You guys.

256
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:02,780
Put the gifts away.

257
00:13:02,780 --> 00:13:04,390
After today's banquet,

258
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:06,300
