259
00:13:06,870 --> 00:13:07,510
Yes, sir.

260
00:13:07,510 --> 00:13:08,270
Wait.

261
00:13:08,780 --> 00:13:10,150
Since I likened this to a wedding banquet,

262
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:11,750
