266
00:13:15,900 --> 00:13:17,750
Boy, get me some paper and a brush.

267
00:13:17,750 --> 00:13:18,900
Do list your names

268
00:13:18,900 --> 00:13:20,390
and your gifts on the paper provided.

269
00:13:24,390 --> 00:13:24,990
All right.

270
00:13:31,150 --> 00:13:32,660
Official Zhong, you...

271
